title: Doctor Who Unleashed (2017) Chapter 1 - 1963
description:
**IN COLOR**

Updated and in 720x400 widescreen
See the new and improved Peter Cushing Doctor Who Saga.

The updated story means that Peter Cushing is now playing the part of a young William Hartnell. I wont spoil what I've done by telling you any more. 

The Doctor (Peter Cushing) is an eccentric mad professor in 1963, he and his grand daughter are about to embark on the trial of their latest invention - T.A.R.D.I.S - and with his unwilling accomplice in disbelief, and convinced of the scientists insanity, surrounded by peril will this bunch of soft centers survive???

Stars Peter Cushing
      Roberta Tovey
      and many more

Guest Stars
      Peter Capaldi
      Jenna-Louise Coleman
      and many more
